<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; background: #f4f0ea; margin: 0; padding: 40px 20px; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; }
        .header {
            background: #0D0D0D;
            padding: 32px 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 32px;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            color: #C9A84C;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .logo span { color: #F5F0E8; }
        .body { padding: 40px; }
        h2 { color: #0D0D0D; font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        p { color: #666; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .recap {
            background: #fafafa;
            border-left: 3px solid #C9A84C;
            padding: 24px 28px;
            margin: 28px 0;
        }
        .recap-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .recap-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .recap-label { color: #999; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .recap-value { color: #333; font-weight: 600; }
        .recap-value.gold { color: #C9A84C; }
        .footer {
            background: #0D0D0D;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Peaky<span>Barber</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="body">
            <h2>Réservation confirmée ✓</h2>
            <p>Bonjour <strong>{{ appointment.clientName }}</strong>,</p>
            <p>Votre rendez-vous a bien été enregistré. Voici le récapitulatif :</p>

            <div class="recap">
                <div class="recap-row">
                    <span class="recap-label">Service</span>
                    <span class="recap-value gold">{{ appointment.service.name }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="recap-row">
                    <span class="recap-label">Coiffeur</span>
                    <span class="recap-value">{{ appointment.barber.name }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="recap-row">
                    <span class="recap-label">Date & Heure</span>
                    <span class="recap-value gold">{{ appointment.appointmentAt|date('d/m/Y à H:i') }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="recap-row">
                    <span class="recap-label">Durée</span>
                    <span class="recap-value">{{ appointment.service.duration }} minutes</span>
                </div>
                <div class="recap-row">
                    <span class="recap-label">Tarif</span>
                    <span class="recap-value">{{ appointment.service.priceFormatted }}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p>En cas d'empêchement, merci de nous contacter le plus tôt possible.</p>
            <p>À très bientôt,<br><strong>L'équipe Peaky Barber</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            © {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Peaky Barber — Tous droits réservés
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
